Brief hacking guide to Duff
===========================

Important files
===============

duff.c
  Program main, information printing and primary driver logic.

duffentry.c
  Functionality for dealing with 'entries', i.e. collected files.

duffstring.c
  Replacement implementations of various libc string functions.

duffutil.c
  Error reporting and various other small utilities.

sha1.c
  Implements SHA1 checksum calculation.

duff.h
  Main header file.

duffstring.h
  Header for replacement libc function implementations.

sha1.h
  Header for SHA1 code.


Important functions
===================

duffentry.c: compare_entries()
  The main comparison function for entries.  Start there if you wish to
  hack the comparison algorithm.

duff.c: process_path(), recurse_directory() and stat_file()
  The main functions for collecting files and making entries.  Start
  there if you wish to hack the traversal algorithm.


